text: Emma Wright (born 16 November 1996) is a Canadian water polo player. She participated at the 2013 World Aquatics Championships, 2015 Pan American Games, 2013 World Aquatics Championships, and 2013 World Aquatics Championships. She plays for University of California's women's water polo team. == References == Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian water polo players
